Summary
Edgar Nathaniel Sarratt III, known professionally as midwxst, is an American rapper and singer born on June 5, 2003, in Columbia, South Carolina. Raised in Indianapolis, Indiana, Sarratt grew up in a military family and faced various relocations, which instilled adaptability and resilience. He was diagnosed with ADHD at a young age, which influenced his approach to music and creativity. In high school, he began producing music in his bedroom, initially under the alias $uspect, and later adopting the stage name midwxst.
